- `TryBuildStructure(structureId, builderUnitId, buildingSize, targetPos, directionPos, padding, bypassTownCenterPadding)`
- `FindBestPosition(buildingSize, targetPos, direction, padding, bypassTownCenterPadding)`
- `QueueBuildingRequest(structureId, buildingSize, targetPosition, priority, padding, bypassTownCenterPadding, builderUnitId, requireScouting)`
